Here's my famous spaghetti carbonara recipe:

Ingredients:
- 400g spaghetti
- 200g pancetta
- 4 egg yolks
- 100g pecorino cheese
- Black pepper to taste

Instructions:
1. Cook pasta in salted boiling water
2. Fry pancetta until crispy
3. Mix egg yolks with grated cheese
4. Toss hot pasta with pancetta
5. Add egg mixture and toss quickly
6. Serve with extra pepper

Enjoy!
Grandma
